mvn test -PprofileName
mvn test -Dtest=LoginTest
✅ What it does:
Overrides default test execution in pom.xml and runs only LoginTest.java.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
mvn test -Dbrowser=chrome
The value chrome is passed to your Java code using System.getProperty("browser").

✅ How to Use It in Code:

String browser = System.getProperty("browser");
System.out.println("Running tests on browser: " + browser);
